%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c.label: TextBlock45
%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c.text: Please select the products for which you want to receive a Medically Underwritten Quote. If you have requested a preliminary quote, then the products which you previously selected are preselected below, however, you may select alternative products for the Medically Underwritten quote. You may select as many products as you wish to quote for, but can only compare up to 3 at a time.
